{"word":"ἀσθενέω","slug":"ἀσθενέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀσϑενέω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀσθενής\">ἀσθενής</a></el>, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀσθένεια\">ἀσθένεια</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘experience weakness’ in body <b><i>be sick</i> <a href='B:470 25:36'>Mt 25:36</a>, <a href='B:470 25:39'>39</a>; <a href='B:490 4:40'>Lk 4:40</a>; <a href='B:500 4:46'>J 4:46</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ oft.\">oft.</a>; <b><a href='B:510 9:37'>Ac 9:37</a>; <a href='B:570 2:26'>Phil 2:26</a>, <a href='B:570 2:27'>27</a>; <a href='B:620 4:20'>2 Ti 4:20</a>; <a href='B:660 5:14'>Js 5:14</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘lack capacity for <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a>’ <b><i>be weak, be deficient</i> <a href='B:520 8:3'>Ro 8:3</a>; <a href='B:520 14:2'>14:2</a>; <a href='B:540 12:10'>2 Cor 12:10</a>; <a href='B:540 13:3'>13:3</a>.</b> In extended sense <b><a href='B:520 4:19'>Ro 4:19</a>; <a href='B:520 14:1'>14:1f</a>;</b> of timidity<b> <a href='B:540 11:29'>2 Cor 11:29</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>3.</pp></b> ‘lack necessities’, <b><i>be in need</i> <a href='B:510 20:35'>Ac 20:35</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀσθένεια\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀσθένημα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}